                "accordion_row_97fDtj": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "¿Qué pasa si estoy entre dos tallas?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_7iKcg4": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>If your footwear is feeling roomy, but the size down is too small, you can customize the fit by adding an insole – this is equivalent to a half-size down. If you’d like to keep the roomier fit of the shoe but have the heel feel more snug, try attaching<a href=\"https://www.drmartens.com/us/en/heel-grips/p/AD034000\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">heel grips</span></a>. These products are available on the<a href=\"https://www.drmartens.com/us/en/accessories/c/07000000?categories=globalproductcatalog_us2dcategories_us2daccessories_us2daccessories2dshoecare2dlaces2dinsoles_us2daccessories2dshoecare2dlaces2dinsoles2dshoecare2dcleaner\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Dr. Martens website</span></a>.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "none",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                        "weight": "",
                        "font_size": "1rem",
