                "accordion_row_4n4XaV": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "¿Cómo sé si estoy usando la talla correcta?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_BtbPiV": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>Start by assessing the fit of your shoes while standing and walking. You’ll know you’re wearing the correct size if the widest portion of your foot is resting in the widest portion of the shoe. Everyone’s toes are shaped differently, but you want enough space for all of your toes to lay flat and not feel crunched against the front when you walk. It is normal for your heel to rise slightly in a new pair – you want your to be able to move naturally and prevent blisters. As you start to wear you pair more, the soles will start to flex with your foot.<br/><br/>The stiffer the leather, the longer it will take to break in your boots or shoes. You can find an overview of our leather variations here in our<a href=\"https://www.drmartens.com/us/en/guides/our-leathers\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">leather guide</span></a>. If you are still breaking in your boots or shoes, give it some time; it will all be worth it.<br/><br/><strong>Tip:</strong>Some snugness is okay, but not necessary. Painful tightness can indicate the need for a different size or style. Try using our<a href=\"https://www.drmartens.com/us/en/wonder-balsam-shoe-protector-85ml/p/AC787000\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Wonder Balsam Shoe Protector</span></a>to protect, condition, clean, and help your new footwear shape to your feet.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "none",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                        "weight": "",
                        "font_size": "1rem",
                        "font_size_mobile": "",
                        "line_height": "loose",
                        "letter_spacing": "normal",
                        "case": "none",
                        "wrap": "pretty",
                        "font_stretch": "normal",
                        "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                        "color_custom": "",
