                },
                "accordion_row_EyDVkz": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "¿Cuáles son los mejores DM para pies anchos?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_8VJiyq": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>Our Unisex and Men’s standard fit footwear offers a wider and rounded toe shape, making it ideal for individuals with broader feet. Our Women’s standard fit styles will fit slightly smaller, and fit closer to traditional Women’s sizing. These styles have a narrower footbed. For example, if the 1460 Women’s Smooth Leather Lace-Up Boots feel too narrow, we suggest trying the 1460 Smooth Leather Lace-Up Boots in unisex sizing. Many people find that it offers that extra bit of space they need for the best fit.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "none",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                        "weight": "",
